    <div class="body">
        <p>When using IIS7 and the url rewrite module with this server, a call to getPathInfo returns the UNENCODED_URL key from $_SERVER</p>

<p>The issue is this value is NOT urldecoded, where PATH_INFO is required to be urldecoded (see the spec), leading to issues when the same code must run cross system</p>

